Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:09.31,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是連前進軌道都無法改變的幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:13.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:17.65,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟、被「命運」所束縛的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:24.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將它重寫、因為若能看見你和未來 不是最棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！我只想在戰鬥中成長 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.29,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,擊穿陰天！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.46,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍舊熊熊燃燒 雷鳴撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.30,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除夢魘 看見未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,過去、未來、還有如今當下、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏懼過去 現在為了被托付的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的驕傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:48.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想看到眼淚、所以要不斷嘶吼！一直永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:52.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會墮落！因為揚起的風會讓我凌駕於命運之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:59.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身後、有著想要守護的笑容！ 永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.62,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了彼此！我會揍飛你心中的痛苦！讓悲傷什麼的永遠安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:06.74,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}無論多少次…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:34.91,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光搖曳 我們未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:42.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會實現 描繪明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠不會磨滅 銘記在心中的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:55.77,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是無盡的淚水能掩蓋傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:04.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就無需畏懼 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:13.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向著無邊無際的天空 張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:19.12,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那輪皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:24.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲傷 也要懷著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:29.30,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算無法回頭 也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生輝的夢想 閃耀在探索的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:41.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最寶貴的那份思念 仍舊在延續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:47.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裏 我們都一起走過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:55.58,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心靈之匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 這裏就交給魔法師們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來負責護送
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 請讓我留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有看到最後的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 請看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是未來的我所留下的筆記本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一這個時代的大門遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼未來的日蝕之門也會不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連鎖反應下 我的存在也會被抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 如果現在這個時代的大門被破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼未來也會被改寫成「大門已經被破壞的未來」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來也就不會有大門存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣 羅格就沒有辦法來到這個時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…這能夠阻止已經發生了的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍和羅格都會從這個時代消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼破壞那麼巨大的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是個輕鬆的活兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果羅格沒從未來過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界就會回到原本的歷史軌跡上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是為了遵守和未來的我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把僅存的魔力都用上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二門的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃道十二宮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…毫無效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是用超強抗魔力耐性的超魔力合金製成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能這麼簡單就被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}黃金草原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快從我們的時代…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 現在的羅格怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我會和我成為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同影子和影子重疊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算剝奪羅格的未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有阿庫諾羅基亞在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才會來這裏創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 在這個瞬間 他一定很慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有關係的 有我在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的 反正一年後也會死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有保護他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是沒能保護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在他還是活著的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是只會陪貓玩的那個我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有品嚐過絕望的傢伙是無法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道得到這個千載難逢的希望後 我有多麼瘋狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是讓過去被絕望籠罩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能讓所有的人都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟點吧 夏·多拉格尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是事實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都有選擇未來的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 要繼續我們所選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是你選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天會怎樣 就算不知道也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了竭盡全力活在現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了啊 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妖精的尾巴的魔法師 夏·多拉格尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一名滅龍魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的煌炎 咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏  已經…無計可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有那種事 一定還有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對…不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會逃 也不會退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還遠遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這大門也太結實了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這樣都毫髮無損
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快離開大門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大門被破壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然將超魔力合金的門給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後會怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據計算 未來的門會變得無法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 羅格無法來到這個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史會恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發出了光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回到原來的時代了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要捲起尾巴逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區人類 區區人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建造了連接時空之門的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擾亂了各位自然時間的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生活在400年前 而我們生活在現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來應該是毫無爭鬥理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而將此扭曲了的正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠·E·費歐雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和你的身體顏色一樣的翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說…一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠之龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠之龍…聽上去挺不錯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 被蒙過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,898)}我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定…了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記你的 夏·多拉格尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小型龍消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一頭霧水 但看來是結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夏哥 一定是夏哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了呢 伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滅龍魔法師沒有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正打倒了龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉被稱為滅龍魔法師了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那麼強啊 所謂的龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕阿庫諾羅基亞會更強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 現在別想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 雖然沒有勝利的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之戰鬥結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勝利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護了同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識的羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會成為「你」的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子…想要吞噬我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少次 多少次地纏上我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在失去弗洛的那天 我與影子成為了一體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一年後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要告訴「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年後 一定要守護弗洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——殺掉了弗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是…哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也都在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 繼續冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淚水…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,555)}謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 聽我說哦 有大新聞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嘛哈比 慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為拯救了王國的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王大人好像要設宴招待我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是設在宮殿裏的宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會有很多好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如照燒火焰的 又或是干蒸火焰之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…恐怕有點難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話 大型舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 烤全火好像也不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說拿火焰當食材 到底是什麼腦回路啊

